# Frontend Storybook (`apps/storybook`)

Visual workshop for `@repo/ui` and `@repo/metadata-ui`. App wiring: `frontend-app.mdc`. Layers: `agent-discipline.mdc`.

## Scope (stay here for visual work)

- Introduction, Metadata UI galleries, UI Compose, Primitives
- Theme Studio previews via story decorators — not production route changes
- Mocks in `.storybook/mocks/` (navigation, i18n)

Do **not** refactor `packages/ui/.../compose/workspace/**` for Storybook contrast or polish. Fix preview decorators, parameters, or story layout instead.

## Story conventions

- CSF3 stories; co-locate decorators when a story needs shell chrome
- Semantic design tokens in story `className` — no ad-hoc hex or raw pixel hacks
- Compose galleries: use registry/manifest paths documented in `apps/storybook/README.md`
- `a11y.test: 'error'` tiers must pass in `test:stories`

## Anti-patterns

- Flattening `workspace-shell.surfaces.ts` for preview contrast
- Changing `sidebarVariant` defaults to match a story experiment
- Duplicating metadata-ui render logic in stories — import from `@repo/metadata-ui`

## Verification

```bash
pnpm --filter storybook typecheck
pnpm --filter storybook check:theme-css      # preview.css / token integration
pnpm --filter storybook check:storybook-visual-tokens
pnpm --filter storybook test:stories         # axe + interactions
pnpm --filter storybook check:build          # before large story additions
```

Dev: `pnpm --filter storybook dev`. See `apps/storybook/README.md` for visual regression commands.
